{"id":210776,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":1,"day":9}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"271","ytitle":"","mtitle":"“去吧!孩子!”","ftitle":"——记南京大学中文系主任方光","authors":["阿红"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焘先生一段谈话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天，我从学校回去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在门前曬暖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着“新华日报”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仔细地翻看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“响应祖国号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加军事干校!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这两排红字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么光辉荣耀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁在屋里争吵:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我去，你年纪小。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呦，爱国又不分大小!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里很奇怪:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我底两个孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大的十九，小的十七，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他俩要到那里去?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大孩子接着说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我长的壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我考炮兵学校；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你?个子矮，年龄不够……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩子生气了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连忙插嘴:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我不听你的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我偏要去报名!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去吧，孩子!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国需要你们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去吧，孩子!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你父亲不阻拦!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好的河山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容敌人进犯!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们要站在最前线!"}]}